            <title>「萬代食玩 x 潮玩探索之旅」，旺角 T.O.P 化身潮玩熱點，</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/15/toptoys/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=toptoys</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/15/toptoys/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 15 Mar 2025 09:00:57 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1297803</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-16dba41 r-1adg3ll r-1b5gpbm r-a8ghvy" dir="ltr"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-a8ghvy">由 2024 年 3 月 14 日至 31 日，旺角 T.O.P 商場將搖身一變成為全城矚目的潮玩熱點，萬代食玩（BANDAI CANDY TOY）首次聯手萬代潮玩（BANDAI ART TOY，又稱 BNESH 原創商品），舉辦「萬代食玩 x 潮玩探索之旅」（Bandai Candy Toy x Art Toy Adventure）活動。活動以「冒險」為主題，將整座商場從 MTR/F 至 3/F 精心打造成一個超大型動漫樂園，各樓層設有特色打卡位及展品，讓訪客彷彿置身於一場驚喜連連的探索之旅，集觀賞、購物與娛樂於一身，為動漫迷及市民帶來前所未有的體驗。</span></span></div><div dir="ltr"></div><div dir="ltr"><a title="IMG_5295" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54389641504/in/album-72177720324461119" data-flickr-embed="true"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54389641504_0c940d3eb4_h.jpg" alt="IMG_5295" width="1280" height="1600" /></a></div><div dir="ltr"><a title="DSC00024" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54389679158/in/album-72177720324461119" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54389679158_e8bdca2d24_h.jpg" alt="DSC00024" width="1600" height="1066" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><div dir="ltr"></div><h2 class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-rjixqe r-b88u0q" dir="ltr"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-b88u0q r-a8ghvy"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-a8ghvy">活動亮點：1.8 米高「突擊自由高達極」立像首度亮相海外</span></span></span></h2><div class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-rjixqe r-b88u0q" dir="ltr"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-a8ghvy">活動的最大焦點莫過於海外首次亮相的全高 1.8 米的 FW GUNDAM CONVERGE「突擊自由高達極」立像。這座以《機動戰士高達 SEED FREEDOM》劇場版主角機為藍本的立像，搭配充滿科技感的設計地台，完美重現劇中機體的英姿，勢必成為粉絲爭相拍照的打卡熱點。隨著劇場版熱潮持續升溫，這款立像繼去年「飛昇自由高達」掀起話題後，再次為高達迷帶來震撼視覺享受。</span></span></div><div dir="ltr"></div><div dir="ltr"><a title="DSC09904" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54388574427/in/album-72177720324461119" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54388574427_140cff5091_h.jpg" alt="DSC09904" width="1600" height="1066" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="DSC09838" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54389644639/in/album-72177720324461119" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54389644639_95ad7f2591_h.jpg" alt="DSC09838" width="1600" height="1066" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><h2 class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-rjixqe r-b88u0q" dir="ltr"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-b88u0q r-a8ghvy"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-a8ghvy">期間限定店與人氣商品</span></span></span></h2><div class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-rjixqe r-b88u0q" dir="ltr"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-a8ghvy">活動期間，場內不僅展出多款人氣及限定商品，更設有期間限定店，讓訪客可即時購買心儀的動漫周邊，實現「睇得買得又玩得」的全方位體驗。兩款先行發售商品更將於活動期間搶先登場：</span></span></div><div dir="ltr"><h2 class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-rjixqe r-16dba41" dir="ltr"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-b88u0q r-a8ghvy"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-a8ghvy">G FRAME FA 第 08MS 小隊 SPECIAL SELECTION</s